@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bwqrav(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.46 - v1)
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.33) + v2)
    v2 = wp.exp(v1)
    tmp = ((v2 / (v2 + 0.66 + tmp + 0.01)) - v2)
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.63)))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.82) / (v2 + 0.28 + v1 + 0.75)) - (v2 * v0))
    v0 = (0.31 * v1)
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
